{"tid":1628741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［咪再做港豬]屌哂你地，唔好再屈手足係popo","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:28:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T06:00:18.000Z","uid":326052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ed4b8a15f2e11399e54db258fe05a785317ed895","tid":1628741,"uid":326052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZfAXPTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZfAXPTu.jpg&h=15356e65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是咁的，我見好多地方都話呢位手足係popo（利申，識佢本人，吊左佢咪淨帶口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌哂你地老母</span></span>，上下圖擺明兩個人都可以話係同一個人，要唔要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">去驗下眼</span>，捉鬼捉到傻撚哂。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">手足比人當係popo知唔知有幾侮辱</span></span></em></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋出面係咁話觀塘站唔關事，中移動，360又話唔係自己人做，做得出怕咩認，就係因為仆街政府繼續唔回應，我地先至咁做，家下係咁割蓆，同對家有咩分別！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵爆炸都唔割</span></span><br />\n我地做得出就唔怕認<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"7d31e46ab0a6a96c908d54c49916db2e7e3ffcc6","tid":1628741,"uid":326052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:37:29.000Z","msg":"自推01"},{"pid":"087a8c9bb2a4d5694e5f5a475f4d824b0cd45b01","tid":1628741,"uid":326052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:37:40.000Z","msg":"自推02"},{"pid":"d55e0d4d8f69a044be0f23685c26f2f093dc2102","tid":1628741,"uid":326052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT